14. Qb3
14. d5 {This is the point. We are unable to trap the knight on b4 and Black is fighting back in the center. We are lagging behind in development.} 
15. Ba3
15. a5
16. bxa6
16. bxa6
17. Bxb4
17. Qb6 {Black wins back the piece on b4.} 
18. Nbd2
