18. Qxe5
19. Rxe5 {We reach some kind of an equal endgame but it is still imbalanced. Our pawns on the queenside are well advanced and the c7-pawn is a clear weakness.} 
19. Bg6
20. gxf3
20. Bxd3
21. Rc1 {Position is equal although Black is the one who has to show more precision to hold the draw.} 
