19. Re3 {We want to go Ne1 next. Black has to do something quick here.} 
19. Qd5 {Black gives up the c7-pawn but ends up winning back one of the bishops.} 
20. Bxc7
20. Nb5
21. Bxb5
21. Qxb5
22. Nd2 {We will exchange the e4-knight and also protect the pawn on b2. The bishop on d3, although it looks great, does not do a lot of stuff. We can start an attack on the kingside in the future.} 
