11. Bxe3
12. Rxe3
12. g5 {This is an amazing resource pointed out by the engines at high depth. I left the computer running for a while and suddenly this move popped up. It turns out that we will miss the dark-squared bishop when we try to exploit Black's kingside expansion.} 
13. Nh2 {We stop the move g4. Next, we want to go for the d4 break and also bring our other knight to g3. But the problem is that we cannot put much pressure on the center after having played the move Nh2.} 
