14. Nh5
15. Be3 {We will exchange the bishops and go for d4.} 
15. Nhf4
16. N1h2
16. Qf6
17. Kh1 {We have two nice plans to kick out the knight. Going for h3-h4 or Ng1 followed by g3. This is the problem with both the knights fighting for the same square.} 
